longBusinessSummary: QAF Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the manufacture and distribution of bread, bakery, and confectionery products in Singapore, Australia, the Philippines, Malaysia, and internationally. It operates through Bakery, Distribution and Warehousing, and Investments and Others segments. The company is involved in the trading, agency, and distribution of food and beverage products; and provision for warehousing logistics services of food items. It also offers various frozen and par-baked specialty breads and pastries; and a range of bread and kaya spreads under the Delicia, Cowhead, and Auntie Rosie's brand names, as well as operates cold storage warehouse. The company was formerly known as Ben and Company Limited and changed its name to QAF Limited in 1984. QAF Limited was founded in 1950 and is based in Singapore.
